ass=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:00:38.000Z","msg":"Mk妹 細路女 睇你咩圈子姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:04:29.000Z","msg":"咁又係<br />\nGolf 照計都溝到大部分女"},{"pid":"f5e38af1df78d280b96f896f11597051d6ec7cfd","tid":712091,"uid":17515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72ae1a8f901ebcaa8b9eca2d010dc48c646f45ba","tid":712091,"uid":52617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62e50cd335c61626e831e5ed237b9890463ce8f7","tid":712091,"uid":190902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:06:50.000Z","msg":"同埋除咗vw之外, bmw車都好多, 香港人真係好撚有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:10:14.000Z","msg":"周街都 323i <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"舊寶馬就多左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   新版果d 邊布可能"},{"pid":"367f20020ac8180d69c7bcd99af4c84ad58faa7c","tid":712091,"uid":8717,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"6461ab06ab7c421354c58a2e6f7f5495a5624a18","tid":712091,"uid":45945,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:58:46.000Z","msg":"同樣價錢<br />\n自然會諗歐洲車<br />\n<br />\n之前諗住換車<br />\n本來諗住買 Odyssey<br />\n但同樣 4x萬可以買到 Tiguan Allspace 7<br />\n真係心郁郁架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:29:05.000Z","msg":"如果第六同第七個位經常有成年人坐既話唔會諗Tiguan, 反之亦然, 似乎唔係替代品, 可能係巴打你個心味清楚自己想要咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n老老實實個人覺得日本車去到30萬以上又另一個世界.而點解我會拎GOLF同JAZZ講, 某程度係覺得日系車過份層次分明, 20萬頭既車或者OPTION可以俾足你, 但大多數行車質感粗糙, 隔音唔落功夫, 門版單簿, 音響喇叭嘈夾拆, 中控及錶版附近感覺空洞, 踏落油門都唔太實在, 總之好似要同用家講我地唔係做唔到, 但平車就係咁, 要好請買中級車. <br />\n<br />\n相反VW車即使你買到入門既POLO/GOLF都唔會有以上既感受, 唔係話Golf會同CC, Tiguan一樣, 但至少落差唔會太大. 成個感覺即使唔係一流都叫到位, 似乎日系品牌暫時得Mazda 做到vw果種下放d好野俾入門車系既感覺 (但佢入門車價錢己經唔入門).<br />\n<br />\n同埋Golf咁好賣我諗係唔少渣緊既人本身都係睇日本車仔先,係試完車先改變主意. <br />\n<br />\n利申:屋企件老野都係臨買Spade前睇完車展轉o太買Golf. 日日笑鳩我架日本車垃圾過線都腳軟."},{"pid":"91f3544253761bef8be6c268803e232f9e0310ae","tid":712091,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d2f8c8262de3904bec8106124fdf2cb14e72bbb","tid":712091,"uid":75766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92b06dc082aeecbd54dd35b578b5450cb1d62a10","tid":712091,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:02:15.000Z","msg":"Lexus越嚟越貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:43:06.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係個啲價位 反而高端市場仲平左 新LS平左好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"NX貴咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121510d6cab896a99b2c72ed4eae5fd6ed20bdea","tid":712091,"uid":190902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5e38af1df78d280b96f896f11597051d6ec7cfd","tid":712091,"uid":17515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72ae1a8f901ebcaa8b9eca2d010dc48c646f45ba","tid":712091,"uid":52617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62e50cd335c61626e831e5ed237b9890463ce8f7","tid":712091,"uid":190902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:06:50.000Z","msg":"同埋除咗vw之外, bmw車都好多, 香港人真係好撚有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T05:10:14.000Z","msg":"周街都 323i <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"舊寶馬就多左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   新版果d 邊布可能"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"10年附近算唔算舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0893ae55a6a690909a9516eee0dd2e85cc5f3d9","tid":712091,"uid":190902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"121510d6cab896a99b2c72ed4eae5fd6ed20bdea","tid":712091,"uid":190902,"like":0,"