手離場都唔洗蝕<br />\nHIACE果陣2手價好硬<br />\n5年車都可以賣到25萬之類<br />\n<br />\n咁去試車啦<br />\n嘩我屌呀<br />\nhiace一路開車一路同煎我雙蛋<br />\n坐住係引擎上面真係好撚ON9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nD位窄都算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條避震....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身都諗住 貨VAN係咁架啦 是鳩但啦<br />\n見有時間 D車行又係晒果邊 (九龍灣)<br />\n咪順便睇下又試下車<br />\n試一試VITO....嘩我屌呀....<br />\n咁撚舒服既<br />\n價錢中要平過HIACE<br />\n再過隔離福士.....部T6果陣岩岩轉款<br />\n真係好撚型<br />\n然後再試埋車<br />\n上網睇左D資料....<br />\n最後扑左鎚部T6<br />\n真心...個人駕駛感覺好好多<br />\n空間夠 設備齊 (雙電門, LED轉向頭燈 等) <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要平過部HIACE...<br />\n真係唔明hiace個價仲企咁硬做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係既 你話咩波箱易壞 冇零件要訂 整車又貴等等<br />\n喂大老你HIACE唔會壞咩?<br />\n我寧願係我渣車既果幾萬公里入面係享受<br />\n開HIACE真係唔係幾享受到個駕駛感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6425cbf3f7ecd4eaff59e6a545fb34e8eb67c5","tid":712091,"uid":15199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:55:02.000Z","msg":"多左好多passat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a799545ea84fdcddccd204ccb45db547fd78188","tid":712091,"uid":122117,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:57:08.000Z","msg":"之前recall過<br />\n波箱偈油成日出問題 唔好買呀<br />\n<br />\n利申 Part time VW Custom service<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fd48d90c4abaf8b1528f1ae9a4eff8421a034c","tid":712091,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af9b17ef9f421ef515577882cce3360c291a8cea","tid":712091,"uid":46595,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyT